title: Kitchen 168
typeOfFood: Chinese, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Modern Chinese fast food outlet. Has a dedicated vegetarian/vegan menu. All sauces used are vegan suitable except for Malaysian sauce. Egg noodles and hokkien noodles do not contain egg. Honey flavour used is is a sweet syrup, containing no actual honey. A separate wok and burner is used to prepare vegan meals.
streetAddress: Shop 48, Carrum Downs Shopping Centre, 100 Hall Rd
